    // SIZE
    mdc-grid-cell(span="12")
      section
        h5(id="cardsize") Size
        p.
          Cards don’t come with a predefined width or height. They expand horizontally to 
          fill all available space, and vertically to fit their contents.
        p.
          You can set height and width for a card like this:

    mdc-grid-cell(span="6")
      pre
        code-prism.
          &lt;mdc-card
            height="150px"
            width="300px"&gt;
          &lt;/mdc-card&gt;
      
      p Content will be bottom-aligned if it’s smaller than the height of the card.

    mdc-grid-cell(span="6" align="middle")
      mdc-card(height="150px" width="300px")
        mdc-card-title(title="Card title" subtitle="Subtitle")


    mdc-grid-cell(span="12")
      p.
        If you’d like to maintain a consistent height and width across cards, 
        set it in your styles:

    mdc-grid-cell(span="6")
      pre
        code-prism(language="css").
          .my-card-container .mdc-card {
            height: 120px;
            width: 300px;
          }
      pre
        code-prism.
          &lt;div class="my-card-container"&gt;
            &lt;mdc-card&gt;
              ..
            &lt;/mdc-card&gt;
            &lt;mdc-card&gt;
              ..
            &lt;/mdc-card&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

    mdc-grid-cell(span="6" align="middle")
      .my-card-container
        mdc-card
          mdc-card-title(title="Card 1" subtitle="Subtitle")              
