          Media items are designed to be used in horizontal blocks, taking up a fixed height, 
          rather than stretching to the width of the card.
        p.
          Note: Unlike media blocks, media items are not designed to be used as optional containers.
        pre
          code-prism.
            &lt;img class="mdc-card__media-item mdc-card__media-item--1dot5x" src="images/16-9.jpeg"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;

