    mdc-grid-cell(span="12")
      p.
        There are several predefined media item sizes you can use:

      table.property-list
        thead
          tr
            th Class
            th Description
        tbody
          tr
            td mdc-card__media-item
            td Defines a media item and sets it to the default height of 80px.
          tr
            td mdc-card__media-item--1dot5x
            td Sets the media item height to 120px.
          tr
            td mdc-card__media-item--2x
            td Sets the media item height to 160px.
          tr
            td mdc-card__media-item--3x
            td Sets the media item height to 240px.
